<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11013</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那条龙吃了我的马！”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跪倒在地。“我要怎么去西天呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这一路上有这么多危险！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大笑：“师父，你担心的太多了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你这一路上会有很多危险的，但你有我啊！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38565</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我是花果山的大王。我会保护你的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我打败了所有的天兵天将 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你为什么担心一条龙呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空踏入了水里，拿出了他的金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55159</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58895</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要让那条龙从水里出来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58896</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他低头看着水面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妖龙！立刻给我出来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69814</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那条龙从水里跳了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69815</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你敢对着我大吼大叫！你是谁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是谁不重要！”悟空大叫，“ 把马还给我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空举起金箍棒朝那条龙打下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89689</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖龙转身用尾巴挡住了金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93825</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一阵水花飞溅，他又返回了水底。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93826</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空用力跺脚，朝着河面大叫：“胆小鬼！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们怎么办？”唐僧问，“我现在没有马了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111332</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空点点头。“那条妖龙在河里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们就没办法过河。我来试试其他办法。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空用他的金箍棒搅动河水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126216</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>水势变猛，波涛翻滚，发出了巨大的响声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波浪把河底的泥沙都带了上来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快整条河都变得非常浑浊了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138476</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那条龙再次出现。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138477</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你到底在干什么？”他高叫，“我要小睡一会儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还我们马！”悟空命令说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不还！”那龙大叫，“我已经吃了那匹马！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158149</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空再次朝那条龙打下去，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158150</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但那条龙又一次消失在了水里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空对着河面叫喊了三个多小时。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他高声喊着所有难听的话，但那条龙没有再出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176175</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空爬上了河岸，坐在唐僧的身边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186317</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那条龙太难对付了。我不怕他，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190673</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但我也没办法打败他。我需要帮助。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190674</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁能帮你呢？”唐僧问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空想了一会儿：“观音菩萨说过，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果我需要帮助，我可以去找她。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好！”唐僧说，“她也跟我说过一样的话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空想到了自己的头箍，看了唐僧一眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218323</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她已经帮了你了。她给了你这个头箍嘛。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空叹了口气，“ 现在已经不重要了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你在这里等着。我去去就来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空飞身而起，一路向南飞去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238964</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快他就到了南海普陀山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243576</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨正在她宝塔旁边的园子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好！悟空。”她说，“你们的西天之旅怎么样了？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253550</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你头上戴了头箍。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253551</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258526</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，这都是拜您所赐呀！”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258527</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨笑了。“你需要这头箍，悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你太暴力，太残忍了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空转了转眼珠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270598</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧！我来这里是因为我们遇上麻烦了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们在一条宽阔的大河旁边遇到了一条龙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那条龙把我们的马吃掉了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你没告诉那条龙和你一起走的是唐僧吗？”观音菩萨问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有啊！”悟空说，“怎么了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那条龙是在等你们。因为他在他父亲的宫里放了把火，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我遇到他的时候，他正在受罚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我告诉他要帮助唐僧去西天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是他赎罪的方式。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318950</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空挠了挠脑袋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324210</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你现在告诉我太晚了。他不会从水里出来了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>